      What is the size of woman photo passport?
      The photograph should be in colour and of the size of 2 inch x 2 inch 51 mm x 51 mm . The photoprint should be clear and with a continuoustone quality. It should have full face, front view, eyes open. Photo should present full head from top of hair to bottom of chin.

      What is the size of passport size photo?
      2 x 2 inches
      Resolution, Print Size, and Quality

      The correct size of a passport photo is: 2 x 2 inches (51 x 51 mm)

      What size is a 2x2 photo?
      51 x 51 millimeters
      2x2 inches photo equivalents: metric

      A 2x2 inches square photograph is the same as a 51 x 51 millimeters photograph (photo's width is 51 mm and height is 51 mm). This can also be written as 5,1 x 5,1 centimeters (photo's width 5,1 cm and height 5,1 cm).
